    'description' => 'Format a 2D array of data (rows of named/unnamed values) into a clean aligned text table. Takes headers and rows, returns a formatted table string with column alignment, optional borders, and title. Composes well with csv_table, data_simulator, and data_bin_sorter. Pure function, no side effects.',
